Papers for Publication
======================

Whitepapers and proposals for heads of state, governments, and senior advisors.
Source: Markdown. Published: PDF, DOCX, and Markdown via GitHub.

Papers
------

  12hz-power-grid  The 12 Hz Power Grid Proposal
  entfesselt       The Entfesselt Papers

Quick Start
-----------

  1. Drop your paper.md into papers/<slug>/
  2. Run: make
  3. Run: make publish   (commits + pushes)

Each paper.md begins with a YAML frontmatter block:

  ---
  title: "Your Paper Title"
  subtitle: "Subtitle or tagline"
  author: "David Walther"
  date: "April 2026"
  abstract: |
    One-paragraph executive summary shown on the title page.
  ---

Requirements
------------

  pandoc    https://pandoc.org
  xelatex   (TeX Live or MiKTeX)

Install on Debian/Ubuntu:
  sudo apt install pandoc texlive-xetex texlive-fonts-recommended

Build
-----

  make              Build all PDFs and DOCX files
  make pdf          PDFs only
  make docx         DOCX only
  make list         List all papers
  make clean        Remove dist/
  make publish      Build + git commit + push

Output lands in dist/<slug>.pdf and dist/<slug>.docx
